<div class="mypage-header text-center">
    <h4><b>Beliefs</b></h4>
</div>
    <div class="jumbotron text-Left">
        <h2 class="text-center">What we believe.</h2>
        
            <button type="button" class="btn-belief btn-link" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#WWB1"><p>We believe in God; Eternal and Almighty</p></button>
            <div id="WWB1" class="collapse">
                <p><span style="color:red" class="text-left small">We believe in God Who is the Eternal and Almighty Creator of all things. (Eph 3:9; Gen. 1:1).</span></p>
            </div>
        
        
            <button type="button" class="btn-belief btn btn-link"data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#WWB2"><p>We believe God is One Being of three persons</p></button>
            <div id="WWB2" class="collapse">
                <p><span style="color:red" class="text-left small">We believe God is One Being of three persons, the Father, the Son, and the Holy Spirit. (1Peter 1:2).</span></p>
            </div>
        
         <button type="button" class="btn-belief btn btn-link"data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#WWB3"><p>We believe in the deity of Jesus Christ</p></button>
            <div id="WWB3" class="collapse">
                <p><span style="color:red" class="text-left small">We believe in Jesus Christ, in His being the Son of God, in His virgin birth, in His Deity, 
                and in His resurrection and ascension. (John 3:16; Heb. 1:8; Acts. 1:9; Mat. 28:58).</span></p>
            </div>
        <button type="button" style="text-align:left;" class="btn-belief btn btn-link" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#WWB4"><p>We believe in the Holy Spirit, the Third Person of the Triune God</p></button>
            <div id="WWB4" class="collapse">
                <p><span style="color:red" class="text-left small">We believe in the Holy Spirit, that He is the Third Person of the Triune God and the 
                Divine Spirit through whom the Father and Son work.</span></p>
            </div>
        
            <button type="button" class="btn-belief btn btn-link"data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#WWB5"><p>We believe in the New Birth</p></button>
            <div id="WWB5" class="collapse">
                <p><span style="color:red" class="text-left small">We believe in the New Birth, that, when a sinner comes to God and repents of his sins 
                and receives forgiveness, that he is made a new creation in Christ Jesus. 
                (2 Cor. 5:17; 1Peter 1:23; John 3:3)</span></p>
            </div>
        
            <button type="button" class="btn-belief btn btn-link"data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#WWB6"><p>We believe in the Baptism of the Holy Spirit</p></button>
            <div id="WWB6" class="collapse">
                <p><span style="color:red" class="text-left small">We believe in the Baptism of the Holy Spirit, that it is an endowment of power from 
                on high upon the clean, sanctified life and that it is witnessed to in every case by 
                speaking in tongues as the Spirit gives utterance. 
                (Lu. 24:49; Mat. 3:11; John 7:38, 39; Acts 2:4; Mark 16:17, 18).</span></p>
            </div>
        
            <button type="button" class="btn-belief btn btn-link"data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#WWB7"><p>We believe in Sanctification</p></button>
            <div id="WWB7" class="collapse">
                <p><span style="color:red" class="text-left small">We believe in Sanctification, that it is the cleansing of the heart from inbred sin, 
                the changing of the carnal nature to the divine nature, and that it is wrought by the 
                application of the blood of Jesus Christ through faith and consecration to God and that 
                this experience of grace is subsequent to the new birth. 
                ( John 17:15-17; 1 Thes. 4:3; Heb. 2:11; 1 Peter 1:6; Eph. 1:6, 5:25-27; 2 Peter 1:4).</span></p>
            </div>
        
            <button type="button" class="btn-belief btn btn-link"data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#WWB8"><p>We believe in the Bible Signs following believers</p></button>
            <div id="WWB8" class="collapse">
                <p><span style="color:red" class="text-left small">We believe in the Bible Signs following believers. (Mark 16:17; 1 Cor. 14:26).</span></p>
            </div>
        
            <button type="button" class="btn-belief btn btn-link"data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#WWB9"><p>We believe in Water Baptism by immersion</p></button>
            <div id="WWB9" class="collapse">
                <p><span style="color:red" class="text-left small">We believe in Water Baptism by immersion, in the name of the Father, and of the Son, 
                and of the Holy Ghost. (Matt. 28:19; Acts. 8:28,29).</span></p>
            </div>
        
            <button type="button" class="btn-belief btn btn-link"data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#WWB10"><p>We believe in the Divine Church</p></button>
            <div id="WWB10" class="collapse">
                <p><span style="color:red" class="text-left small">We believe in the Divine Church, built by Jesus Christ, that it embraces and includes 
                everyone who is born into the household of faith. 
                (Mat. 16:18; John 3:3; 1 Cor. 12:27; Eph. 2: 19-22).</span></p>
            </div>
        
            <button type="button" class="btn-belief btn btn-link"data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#WWB11"><p>We believe in the Holy Communion</p></button>
            <div id="WWB11" class="collapse">
                <p><span style="color:red" class="text-left small">We believe in the Holy Communion. (1 Cor. 11:23; Luke 22:17-20).</span></p>
            </div>
        
            <button type="button" class="btn-belief btn btn-link"data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#WWB12"><p>We believe in an eternal heaven and an eternal hell</p></button>
            <div id="WWB12" class="collapse">
                <p><span style="color:red" class="text-left small">We believe in an eternal heaven and an eternal hell, that the righteous will live 
                eternally in heaven and the wicked will be eternally punished in the lake that burns 
                with fire and brimstone. (Mat. 25:31-46; Rev. 14:10; Luke 16:24; Matt. 9:43, 44).</span></p>
            </div>
        
            <button type="button" class="btn-belief btn btn-link"data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#WWB13"><p>We believe in the Second Coming of Jesus Christ</p></button>
            <div id="WWB13" class="collapse">
                <p><span style="color:red" class="text-left small">We believe in the Second Coming of Jesus Christ, that it will be visible and literal 
                as His going away. (Acts 1:9-11; John 14:3); that He will first come in the clouds 
                to catch away His waiting Bride. (Mat. 24:40-44; 1 Thes. 4:15-17); and, immediately 
                after the Tribulation to execute judgment upon the ungodly. 
                (Matt. 24:29-31; 2 Thes 1:7-10; Jude 14-16; Zech. 14:3,4).</span></p>
            </div>
        
        <p>*Abbreviated List</p>
    </div>
</asp:Content>
